\\n    - Initialize a new project with package management (e.g., npm init for Node.js).\\n    - Set up version control with Git.\\n\\n4. **Implement Endpoints**:\\n    - Implement CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for todos.\\n\\n5. **Write Unit and Integration Tests**:\\n    - Ensure each endpoint is covered with test cases.\\n\\n6. **Review the Code**:\\n    - Conduct code reviews to ensure quality and maintainability.\\n\\n7. **Deploy the API**:\\n    - Decide on a hosting service (e.g., AWS, Heroku) and deploy the application.\\n\\n8. **Document the API**:\\n    - Provide API documentation for developers to use.\\n\\nI will now create tickets for these tasks on our project board.\",\"type\":\"ThoughtEvent\"},{\"id\":\"1da1ddf8-2e33-413d-b5cd-60c71209cae3\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":805,\"completion_tokens\":361},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T20:46:37.020770Z\",\"content\":[{\"id\":\"call_MY3KnLz50COttnJjU3ZFtFbM\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"data/project_board/todo_api\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_create_directory\"},{\"id\":\"call_HnCRexyXk5dxXDxdpuZ4PL31\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"data/knowledge_base/todo_api\\\"}\",\"name\":\"docs_create_directory\"}],\"type\":\"ToolCallRequestEvent\"},{\"id\":\"7d9f1137-03b8-4270-a1bc-516aa08b0ca0\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T20:46:37.049692Z\",\"content\":[{\"content\":\"Successfully created directory data/project_board/todo_api\",\"name\":\"board_create_directory\",\"call_id\":\"call_MY3KnLz50COttnJjU3ZFtFbM\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Successfully created directory data/knowledge_base/todo_api\",\"name\":\"docs_create_directory\",\"call_id\":\"call_HnCRexyXk5dxXDxdpuZ4PL31\",\"is_error\":false}],\"type\":\"ToolCallExecutionEvent\"}]},\"name\":\"ProjectManager\"}", "sender": "ProjectManager_c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600/c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600", "re