ternal Server Error` on server failure\\n\\n### Get a Single Todo\\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\\n- **Method**: `GET`\\n- **Description**: Retrieve a specific todo by ID.\\n- **Response**:\\n  - `200 OK` on success\\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\\n\\n### Update a Todo\\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\\n- **Method**: `PUT`\\n- **Description**: Update an existing todo.\\n- **Request Body**:\\n  ```json\\n  {\\n    \\\"title\\\": \\\"Buy groceries and more\\\",\\n    \\\"description\\\": \\\"Milk, Bread, Eggs, Butter\\\",\\n    \\\"completed\\\": true\\n  }\\n  ```\\n- **Response**:\\n  - `200 OK` on success\\n  - `400 Bad Request` on validation error\\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\\n\\n### Delete a Todo\\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\\n- **Method**: `DELETE`\\n- **Description**: Delete a todo by ID.\\n- **Response**:\\n  - `204 No Content` on success\\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\\n\\n## Models\\n\\n### Todo\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"1\\\",\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"Buy groceries\\\",\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"Milk, Bread, Eggs\\\",\\n  \\\"completed\\\": false\\n}\\n```\"}", "name": "docs_write_file"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1773175599, "model": "gpt-4o-2024-08-06", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_c4e01d72e0", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 526, "prompt_tokens": 808, "total_tokens": 1334, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}}, "prompt_tokens": 808, "completion_tokens": 526, "agent_id": "CodeReviewer_c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600/c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600"}
