und\\n\\n## Models\\n\\n### Todo\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\"id\\": \\"1\\",\\n  \\"title\\": \\"Buy groceries\\",\\n  \\"description\\": \\"Milk, Bread, Eggs\\",\\n  \\"completed\\": false\\n}\\n```"}', name='docs_write_file')], type='ToolCallRequestEvent')}
