2026-03-11 03:46:56,528 [INFO] autogen_core.events: {"type": "ToolCall", "tool_name": "docs_read_file", "arguments": {"path": "todo_api/api_design.md"}, "result": "# REST API Design for Todo App\n\n## Endpoints\n\n### Create a Todo\n- **URL**: `/todos`\n- **Method**: `POST`\n- **Description**: Create a new todo item.\n- **Request Body**:\n  ```json\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Buy groceries\",\n    \"description\": \"Milk, Bread, Eggs\",\n    \"completed\": false\n  }\n  ```\n- **Response**:\n  - `201 Created` on success\n  - `400 Bad Request` on validation error\n\n### Get All Todos\n- **URL**: `/todos`\n- **Method**: `GET`\n- **Description**: Retrieve a list of all todos.\n- **Response**:\n  - `200 OK` on success\n  - `500 Internal Server Error` on server failure\n\n### Get a Single Todo\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\n- **Method**: `GET`\n- **Description**: Retrieve a specific todo by ID.\n- **Response**:\n  - `200 OK` on success\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\n\n### Update a Todo\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\n- **Method**: `PUT`\n- **Description**: Update an existing todo.\n- **Request Body**:\n  ```json\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Buy groceries and more\",\n    \"description\": \"Milk, Bread, Eggs, Butter\",\n    \"completed\": true\n  }\n  ```\n- **Response**:\n  - `200 OK` on success\n  - `400 Bad Request` on validation error\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\n\n### Delete a Todo\n- **URL**: `/todos/{id}`\n- **Method**: `DELETE`\n- **Description**: Delete a todo by ID.\n- **Response**:\n  - `204 No Content` on success\n  - `404 Not Found` if todo is not found\n\n## Models\n\n### Todo\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"1\",\n  \"title\": \"Buy groceries\",\n  \"description\": \"Milk, Bread, Eggs\",\n  \"completed\": false\n}\n```", "agent_id": "Architect_c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600/c15c0470-08bb-4d29-bac9-f98ff79af600"}
